v1.0.0
  Initial release.

  * Added interfaces for creating a resume from modular sections. Here is a list
    of sections added:
      - projects
      - education
      - work
      - skills
      - contact information
  * Added a styling system for customizing the look of certain parts of the
    resume.
  * Added a template
  * Added `just` recipes to
    - build the project
    - install the project locally
    - run tests
    - clean build directory
    - open test artifacts
    - check built package for Typst packaging compliance
